Subject: [PATCH 9/9] bridge phase 11b: repl_bridge hardening
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Fills in three Phase 6 MVP deferrals identified in the parity plan.

Env recreation on 404 / expired:
- New _recreate_environment() — TS Strategy-2 (fresh session on
  re-registered env). Kills any active session, archives the prior id,
  re-registers via api.register_bridge_environment, creates a fresh
  session via params.create_session. Returns True/False so the poll
  loop can resume vs back off.
- Bounded by params.max_env_recreation_attempts (default 3). Counter
  resets on successful recreation so a future 404 starts fresh.
- Fires 'reconnecting' state during the attempt + 'ready' on success
  or 'failed' on exhaustion.
- Strategy-1 (in-place reconnect_session preserving session id +
  SSE seq-num) deferred — needs reconnect_session API happy path and
  live session-runner resumption, both not yet exercised.

JWT refresh integration:
- New _build_token_refresh_scheduler() — wires TokenRefreshScheduler
  to the spawned session's update_access_token() so long sessions
  receive a fresh ingress JWT via stdin (NDJSON
  update_environment_variables line) before the existing token expires.
- Scheduler armed at spawn, cancelled when session done or torn down.
- get_access_token returns the OAuth token (not the ingress JWT —
  ingress JWT refresh is server-driven via the poll redispatch flow).

Dropped-batch telemetry:
- write_messages / write_sdk_messages bump dropped_batch_count on any
  stdin write failure. Logged with the running count so silent message
  loss is observable in production.

3 new regression tests:
- test_poll_loop_gives_up_after_recreation_exhausted — bounded by
  max_env_recreation_attempts; fires 'reconnecting' + 'failed'
- test_env_recreation_succeeds_and_resets_attempts — happy-path
  recreation resumes polling
- test_dropped_batch_count_increments_on_write_failure — BrokenPipe
  on stdin bumps the counter
- test_jwt_refresh_scheduler_armed_on_spawn — scheduler created at
  spawn, cleared after session done

Existing test_poll_loop_gives_up_on_404 was replaced by the new
recreation-exhausted variant (old behavior obsoleted).

595/595 bridge tests pass (was 592, +3 new).

